{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"af8fa723ec","title":"中央首长第四次接见河南赴京汇报代表团纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8d76d690a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":2,"articleId":"af8fa723ec","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"肖华","id":"06af9ed14a","type":"人物"},{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"刘建勋","id":"3ae36abefb","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘澜涛","id":"3dcf7883ce","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"文敏生","id":"9047f04de9","type":"人物"},{"name":"纪登奎","id":"9a50528209","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"薄一波","id":"d54ab0cc80","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b86c18d775","type":"title","text":"中央首长第四次接见河南赴京汇报代表团纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e72d02f54","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：1967.7.2晚9：40-7.3早1：40，地方：人大会堂安徽厅。中央首长：周总理、康老、肖华、戚本禹、叶群、刘建勋同志出席，总理等人坐在前排。汇报单位：河南二七公社、开封八·二四、河造总、十大总部、河南军区并驻军师级以上部分干部，首都红代会及军事院校部分代表。省委干部、纪登奎、耿其昌、王庭栋。另有：文敏生、赵文甫、杨蔚屏、戴苏理。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d9c9e711e","type":"paragraph","text":"在开会前，由8250等部队首长到纪登奎位前，与纪热情握手。河南军区陈桂昌付司令员与纪亲切交谈。纪：我们早就盼望你来。两人都笑了。刘建勋同志去后，军区司令员张树芝等都去到刘建勋那里交谈。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2606a4fa1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我们刚才商量一下，先听八大总部讲讲。后来的么！（铁军要求发言）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bce4ff31c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有个铁军。那一个讲话？你们准备了没有？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7497048e8","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：……","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d1749e1e3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们是哪一个单位的？","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f632c26d4","type":"paragraph","text":"铁军：十一中的。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1836857121","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们铁军什么时候成立的？","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d1597408d","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：67年2月11日。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64538747c8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们有多少人？","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4398379e6","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：7000人。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86e2a44e21","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这么多，都是郑州的吗？","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aed042113e","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：都是中等学校的。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00718d65b3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：好，你讲吧，时间不要太长。一个同志发言，别的同志不要插话。不要喊口号，对吵，什么“造谣”、“阴谋”。便于弄清是非么！","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd3928f673","type":"paragraph","text":"（全场笑）座谈么！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8b6c334b1","type":"paragraph","text":"（铁军讲到王黎之时）","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7bd94062c7","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：王黎之是什么人？","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8dfc177da","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：是郑州市委第一书记。我们认为他是三反分子，要打倒他。（铁军讲到中学情况时）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4cbbea467","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你是几年级的学生？","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf12c267c3","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：高三的。……（当讲到铁军历史时）","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7b089bb01a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：简单一些。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c67932b3d9","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：……我们听了戚本禹的讲话，给家里的群众作了传达。家里一致有这样的要求，有一些联络员扣压了我们的消息。听汇报的漫不经心。我们说，他们也不记。对我们封锁消息。蒙蔽中央。我们相信中央。但是那些蒙蔽中央的人，绝没有好下场。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3ff1817d9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（大笑）他们没有记录，就不要求他们记录。什么下场不下场！","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b46df3be71","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：（继续攻击二七）","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f79a2e34f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们对二七公社这样对立啊！","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20900329fa","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：我们是两条路线斗争。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ef0d3d9da","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么路线斗争？","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5701a8a077","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：一个要革，一个要保，还不是路线斗争？（气愤的）他们保王黎之（市委书记）","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"091621bf94","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：省里的呢？","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d98d2ab7d6","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：开始我们主张打倒刘建勋……","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a174aa0be7","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（对铁军）对军区怎样啊？","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4fe2fcf09","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：支左大方向基本上是好的，但有严重错误。……我们铁军是革命组织，军区不支持。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f9704c682","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们既然是革命组织，军区不支持，军区大方向又是正确的，这不是矛盾吗？你们讲一下这是什么道理？","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fb507f587","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：（……吞吞吐吐，回答不上来，然后继续讲）","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a3e759fa75","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们认为造总是什么组织？","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc4016f2d6","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：我们基本上认为造总是个造反派组织。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"963e2b2e0f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们中学有造总组织没有？","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5bd323f870","type":"paragraph","text":"铁：有。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b17d076f19","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：公安公社来人了没有？（无人吭声）。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e475757483","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：公安公社的王子现是不是公安公社？","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a317ab41c2","type":"paragraph","text":"王：我是公安公社的成员，我不代表公安公社。","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d5081a072","type":"paragraph","text":"（大笑，并用手指着王子现说）他是公安公社的人，但不代表公安公社。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"171e70fd65","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对总理小声说）那天我批评了公安公社。","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd5f1e6387","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张治安是哪里的？","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37e9cd8342","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我是公安公社的，但代表省直总部。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8206ee89e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（大笑）他是公安公社的人，但不代表公安公社！","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b06935165","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（指王，张二人）那个代表公安公社？","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"251b35cff4","type":"paragraph","text":"（没人吭气）","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93196856f5","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对总理）他不就是公安公社的人吗？","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6dc83d4aff","type":"paragraph","text":"张：……","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6cc4d1c991","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你担任什么工作？","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6655b3f911","type":"paragraph","text":"张：省人事局工作，担任一处秘书。","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3f9435386","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们总部多少人？","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"637351f4c9","type":"paragraph","text":"张：一万九千多人。公安公社是二百九十六人。省直总部包括党群、政法、农村水利、宣传、财贸、工交六个战线。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8befe2936d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们八大总部呢？","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8078bb1d79","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我们和八大总部不是一回事，我们占省直机关总人数的65％。","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c27c5ff175","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：：你们总部主要负责人是谁？","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9db5d03f1","type":"paragraph","text":"张：杨全志。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ddefc5688f","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他是什么人？","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0395c642f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他是工会主席。","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9868a65f6b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：勤务组有多少人？","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0de7d97b95","type":"paragraph","text":"张：十五个人。","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5ec4fa21d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你是个吗？","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff1eb2121d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我是个。","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e4b2a3c95","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：丁石（省监委副书记）参加不参加？","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0fc0c37c84","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他是当权派，没有参加。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92d9b87258","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：杨全志这个人怎么样？","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fb1d4c903","type":"paragraph","text":"张：杨是省直总部的发起人。","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"baf136e218","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：丁石是河造总的吧？","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8e5208c5b","type":"paragraph","text":"张：河造总的（主要讲省直总部的历史）","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"540cc90f4f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候成立的？","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11ad6f685b","type":"paragraph","text":"张：二月二十四日成立，……二七公社根本没有提过炮轰省市委……对刘建勋四月二十四日前提出口号“打倒刘建勋”是应该的，四月二十三日省委机关发出通知“坚决打倒刘建勋”，我们讨论了半个月……我相信中央会正确处理这些问题的。联络员今天给我们扣了打倒刘建勋就是方向错误，刘建勋的问题我们应该揭。","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eca35f40b1","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：刘建勋在八届十一中全会以后在省直机关内有什么表现？","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"687194768e","type":"paragraph","text":"张：没有什么表现……我们没有见到他一次检查。","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8748eebfa","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：也没有支持造反派？写过什么东西没有？","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa3d4dc35d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：八月十九日写了《我的一张大字报》，支持郑大联委。","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e05397b3a3","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：这算不算表现？","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf0353b33a","type":"paragraph","text":"张：算（康老大笑）。","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ac199307dd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：（关于“坚决打倒刘建勋”问题）升级的不是我们，是河造总。河造总之所以这样干，是军区何运洪支持的，我们的录音（攻击刘建勋的）稿是经过军区修改的，录音是省委机关造总发下来的，我们放了十天。","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d0b19f43c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们不在你们组织？","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8774e9df7c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他们是河造总的。来两个代表都在他们那边。","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40194433b5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们省直机关不大办事了。","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdb8827afe","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我们还办公，抓革命促生产，今年的公粮征购很好。（当他谈到当权派来京时）","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09116acb3e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：来了多少人？","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36fe1215a5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：四十多人？有名字的三十八个，还有几个没写上。","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7facddaa9a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：占你们机关人数多少？","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"197b71daf5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：这是走资本主义道路的当权派。","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4614245ba0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：都是走资本主义道路的当权派？","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1fc2e7e4d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：例如张柏园……","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5277f8f242","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：张柏园来北京了？（张柏园是副省长）","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76b1b9e028","type":"paragraph","text":"张：来了。","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ae330a90c","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：住在什么地方？","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8fa351764a","type":"paragraph","text":"张：不知道。","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"482195bcc5","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：张柏园参加了什么组织？","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9679ff712","type":"paragraph","text":"答：什么也没有。","index":95,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"abb56b19e9","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：是他自己来的还是象你说那样，纪登奎、二七公社把他弄来的？","index":96,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1ec1d6185","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是纪打电话，二七公社叫他来的。","index":97,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5c754683a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：在座的有没有知道张柏园住在什么地方？（无人回答）","index":98,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9530cb8c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：我们找他调查材料找不到，是不是在京？","index":99,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e7cccc8c2","type":"paragraph","text":"造总：我们在西苑旅社门口见到他和二七公社的说话。","index":100,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0702238aa","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：二七的谁？叫什么名子？","index":101,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8d35a99b8","type":"paragraph","text":"造总：不知道？","index":102,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b72ad9f628","type":"paragraph","text":"省直：军区镇压运动不支持工人总部，压一派打一派，执行资产阶级反动路线，但军区支左大方向基本是正确的。","index":103,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c7774aa31","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你刚才讲执行了资产阶级反动路线，怎么又说大方向是正确的？","index":104,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52aaa7a6b4","type":"paragraph","text":"省总：我们对反动路线是有抵触的，文、纪公开攻击军区，纪在5.29日向总理汇报12条，在中央首长面前欺骗中央。","index":105,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af46dd904f","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：军区一点不晓得12条？","index":106,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"24bcc4dacf","type":"paragraph","text":"省总：我不知道。","index":107,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db52adda9e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：同情军区的人搞的？还是反对军区的人搞的？关键在这里。","index":108,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86e940b9a3","type":"paragraph","text":"省总：查明是一个有反动言论的人，劳教后到工厂，对军区不满支持二七公社的人搞的。","index":109,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1438eadbf5","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：怎么对军区不满，12条是支持军区的么？那么河南二七公社支持军区吗？","index":110,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92ccb6461d","type":"paragraph","text":"（省直造总继续讲：开始说二七公社是群众组织，后来又说二七公社是御用工具时）","index":111,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4dbf2c055","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你不是刚才讲是群众组织吗？怎么又是御用工具呢？","index":112,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c87d8e610","type":"paragraph","text":"答：它是一个群众组织，但它的作用是御用工具。","index":113,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7390a1ac98","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：到底是一个什么组织？是御用工具还是群众组织？","index":114,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6ee92770e","type":"paragraph","text":"（答：无理狡辩。……）","index":115,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e2a083245","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：那我就明白了。","index":116,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"205566d194","type":"paragraph","text":"郑大战斗师：我们战斗师要求发言。","index":117,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a44dd2849","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是新来的吗？","index":118,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e6ddd9003","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师：从5月1号接到总理指示后就来了，一直没有发言（欲发言）。","index":119,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86eb8e1d4e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你等一等，听总理讲一讲。","index":120,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fe0c72c19","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们等等，十大总部再找一个发言，让工人组织讲，三厂停工了吗？","index":121,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"556bdcad3d","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总代表：没有停，停了一个星期天。","index":122,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc20e73c73","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：（电缆厂复员军人）……","index":123,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9275ac1366","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：七月一日游行是哪个方面的，是你们方面的还是二七、造总方面的？","index":124,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f7a984429","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们十大总部的。","index":125,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"573b5e4f6f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：停产一天吗？","index":126,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00624fba4c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：停了一天。","index":127,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"797234b303","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：抓革命促生产，不能停产闹革命，不要把群众集中起来开大会，过节更应抓革命促生产，不要停工，这不是毛泽东思想，是不符合毛泽东思想的，和学生不一样，学生放假，你们工人不能这样，他们学生么！在学校读书都读呆了，让他们到工人农民中、到社会上去锻炼。你们是工人么，你又是军人么，不应该这样么！不管哪方面，都不应该停产闹革命，这些是违犯毛泽东思想的。挤出时间学毛著，不是集中过多开会，一开会就要打架，不要动不动就把工人拉出来停产打架，什么东西都拿出来了。","index":128,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"658724eaf7","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：（插话）我们没有停产，我们是倒班。","index":129,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"acac148ee1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你这话是说服不了我的，纱厂三班倒么！","index":130,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73b7f2a06e","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：我们停产后又补上了。","index":131,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"220a53a898","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：噢……","index":132,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7b65c7ed49","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：对革命小将看得多了一些，对军区的错误斗争不坚决。","index":133,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3a802003b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：军区宣布郑大联委非法，他们（二七）是你们压的！","index":134,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7264eff76b","type":"paragraph","text":"（省工总想解释）","index":135,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"595dea74c8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们接近官方。","index":136,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4477f41b80","type":"paragraph","text":"（省工总拿出许多照片，污蔑二七公社写反动标语）","index":137,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3aacdaf893","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那是不是他们写的？","index":138,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d5fa50624","type":"paragraph","text":"省总：有照片为证。","index":139,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"903baa24e2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：照片现在有各种照片。我说可能是坏人这样写的，假如别人写的，造他们的谣，给他们脸上抹黑，有没有这种可能呢？","index":140,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6406b6b5a6","type":"paragraph","text":"省工总：（继续讲）……二七公社的骨干组织都是右派势力，的确也有些造反组织。河南军区对工人阶级重视不够，一直不公开支持、不表态，对二七广大革命群众区别对待不够……","index":141,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c5792ed60","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我想问一下铁路。河南铁路几处都中断了，你们三方面说好不好？","index":142,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b329c8a51a","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：不好（河造总、十大总部也说不好）","index":143,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d55b6bafed","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：既然你们三方面都说不好，能不能达成一个协议？使我们的铁路交通能够畅通。","index":144,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"655d0658ab","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我们不知道，与我们无关。","index":145,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"864f19e288","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：这个事我们管不了，不是我们搞的。","index":146,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b924f81a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：豫北纱厂归哪派管？你们这里有没有豫北的？","index":147,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eed1d2fd3c","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我们除了郑州以外，也不管其他地方，他们二七是全省的。","index":148,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dfd8c7ea34","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那不对，听我们念一下我们铁道部军管会的消息……（总理念……）豫北纱厂归哪一派管？","index":149,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4697a82514","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：不知道。","index":150,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c32794fec9","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：不知道。","index":151,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f449552f05","type":"paragraph","text":"（此时二七沉默，全场暂静）","index":152,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b37e4891e6","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：（鹤壁）豫北纱厂不是二七观点，是反二七的，他们听说要宣布他们是保守组织，他要到北京告状、要卧轨、扒车，解放军再三劝说，他们不听。","index":153,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92c757451a","type":"paragraph","text":"（老保着急了，跳起来说：“总理，我要控诉二七公社一小撮混蛋制造反革命停车事件。……”总理摆手制止）","index":154,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc308d4cab","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我要知道的是当前的情况。（老保张口结舌）铁总不停车，工总扒车。","index":155,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d6cd31fdd","type":"paragraph","text":"十大总部：我们只管郑州。","index":156,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2464e62f09","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们八大总部不管全省，河造总呢？","index":157,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f75f7640b1","type":"paragraph","text":"河造总：我们只在郑州。","index":158,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80b6a80452","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们两方都是郑州地区，其他地方都不管了。那末为什么河南那么多地方告急？","index":159,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5e46b0ac2","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：河造总派人到豫北去，对我们二七派的说：“只要你们不打二七旗号，我们就承认你们是造反派，就支持你们。”","index":160,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4925b205e0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：一点不往外发展，我不相信，二七是全省的，那是观点相同么，你们观点不同，那你们为什么派人煽动啊？观点不同就要吵架不行就要打架，打架以后先到郑州，郑州解决不了，就要到北京告状。","index":161,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"145684ca06","type":"paragraph","text":"（老保起哄，抵赖）","index":162,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be81c8269b","type":"paragraph","text":"原因说不完，你们调查一下就知道这么一回事了，你说你们反对停车，那位也反对停车，你是造总的，你说你更加反对，你们三方面都派人立即出发，铁道军管会帮助你们一起去调查。","index":163,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1cbbcbbc9","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：不光是调查，现在的情况是停车了呀！不要光说抓革命促生产，情况是车停了呀。运输不通，总理已讲了，五列，最快车一列，客车一列、货车三列，主要是往北京方面来的，为什么停了，什么原因？是豫北纱厂三百人，要到北京来告状，从今天下午起多次劝说无效，石家庄也是往北京的列车停下了。为什么堵塞？是河南一千二百多工人扒车不讲道理，进行工作无效。第三种情况，洛阳和郑州车站军管会被扒车的人包围了，现在同志们面临着这种情况，车运关系到国计民生，整个国家的问题，面临着这种问题，这不仅是郑州的问题，河南的问题，更不是关系到哪一派的问题，是关系到我们中国的国家问题……总理说包括你们也在内到那里去，说服那里的工人，不能堵塞铁路，有的地方正在卧轨，这是很不好的，保证通车，这是第一个任务，然后再调查情况，发现情况，看是哪一方面的，这是第二个任务，如果光调查，车仍然停着，不如不去，你们要承担这个任务。","index":164,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3aaa854634","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要三方面一道去，康老把任务交待清了，我还说第三个情况，过去二七公社在北京多了一些，因为过去受压迫么，二七现在不要来了，因为中央对二七有一定估价了，要动员在京的二七的人回去，有这些代表就可以了，过去你们不知来了多少次，还有刘建勋在这里，一有问题就来了（二七说还有一二百人），那就好啊！（老保攻击）人家已经承认了这一点，你们还要重复一句。你们作领导还得学习几年么！河南是人多，但人多压力往中央，中央是要讲道理的。","index":165,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6a0ae95f2","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们想人多，跑到中央来几千人，压中央，一压就压垮了，那还象个样子吗？毛泽东思想是不怕压的。","index":166,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78dbdb0612","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我们承认二七公社不会把你们压垮的，不会的。你们犯了错误。他们帮助你们，你们不要想着过去，过去你们压人家了，现在还要压你们。群众组织么！我们都会报告你们走对的，大联合么，都站到毛泽东革命路线上来么！","index":167,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"071178a0a9","type":"paragraph","text":"你们先去打电话，电话不通，你们还是要去的，到石家庄那一千二百多人，那后天就来了，河南太近了，不象四川。你们提出学四川，四川大乱，你们也大乱，各省有各省的特点，河南是中原要地，以后变成毛泽东思想大学校。我们希望各省都有份，同意不同意（答：同意）。第一要打电话，不要扒车，查查是哪个观点的，还是劝他们回去，吃的住的都很不方便，交通也停顿了，铁路关系到工厂，铁路不畅通工厂就窝工了，因为郑州四通八达，郑州这个关键不通，安阳不通，很不利了。","index":168,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6da59d734e","type":"paragraph","text":"现在请郑大后来的讲……","index":169,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfe5d33f84","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师：……","index":170,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63a8155127","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们战斗师多少人？（回答400人），（二七说：原来有1000多）变化了，郑大总数多少人？革联多少人？我问你们和郑大革联在什么问题上有分歧？现在在什么地方？（战斗师说：革联攻击毛主席，林副主席，整总理材料）总理笑着摆手，说具体点，讲你们学校嘛！你们保了些人吗？党委的问题我晓得，工作组来了以后？（战斗师：我们最先反党委），你们两派我都知道，我想听现在。二七公社、郑大联委受压迫，还是你们受压迫？（战斗师扯以前的）不说那些了，军区管制以后，你们那时算非法还是合法？","index":171,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3ff97cc0b","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师：不合法。（革联同学拿出平反传单）","index":172,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3df7db2fa","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：三月六号以后你们还不算合法？那么你们两方面都不合法，为什么不联合起来？恐怕过去太对立了，那时你们两个组织都存在。","index":173,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f36f41a026","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：以后郑州大学没有捕人？郑大学生中被捕的人有没有？（战斗师答只捕三人）党言川不是也被捕了？郑大革联39人（革联：被捕39人）。","index":174,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"729da82d90","type":"paragraph","text":"总理（问战斗师）：你们被捕了多少人？","index":175,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"082e89db0d","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师：没有。","index":176,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"378577dd04","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们两方有没有联合的基础？","index":177,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d36420f39f","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：有！只要他们回到毛主席革命路线上来。","index":178,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df347d541b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：去年在北京也是这个数，后来他们发展了，（指革联），你们减少了。","index":179,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20a4b43b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师（象哭）：我们几乎被压垮了。","index":180,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"305e625a78","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不要那么激动，第一，你们没有被压垮，第二没有被捕。现在你们选择共同基础联合（战斗师继续攻击革联），你们这样互相攻击就没有联合的基础，不是让你们来了吗，你们今后应当怎样做？来两个月要好好学习5.16通知，毛主席的伟大著作，红旗、人民日报社论要好好学习。不是也让你们来了吗？你们今后应该怎么做，你说说前途好了，旧帐少说一点。","index":181,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb74841033","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们三派有一个共同点，一讲就算旧账昨天如何如何，前天如何如何，大前天如何如何，就没有听你讲明天如何如何。你们这些年青人，不象我们这些老头子，我还向前看呢！","index":182,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d94ea39e5","type":"paragraph","text":"（战斗师又摆旧帐）那你不要算旧帐了，还是得向前看，拿这个指导思想，在前进中间看经验教训，不断总结再前进。你们要学习毛主席著作，把你们的思想摆正，毛主席说过：现在的主要任务是革命的大联合嘛！应千方百计地搞好大联合嘛！原则问题当然要弄清楚，看是否有共同点。刚才有四个铁路上的同志都反对停车，这就是共同点嘛，如果你们光算旧帐，等你们把帐算完了，车越停越多！","index":183,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4f1f5fa88","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗师：我们保证和革联同学……但是……","index":184,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29037c9798","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：说了半天，还是算旧帐？","index":185,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be60ef3715","type":"paragraph","text":"（战斗师一面讲，一面把所谓二七打人凶器交给总理），我们就从打人说起吧（战斗师又讲过去）还是过去的事情，你写材料交给联络员（战斗师要求单独汇报）什么单独汇报？！","index":186,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d6eadb683","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们有个抓叛徒组织？有多少人？","index":187,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db798e02ff","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：只限于河南？没有贴大字报公布吧？","index":188,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"129586687d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你先给我一个材料，你们要把抓叛徒的指示好好看一看，好好把那个研究一下，这个问题关系几个组织，这是个严肃的事情，关系到每个人的政治生命。一确定是叛徒就是政治生命的枪毙。千万不要在大街上公布。一个是人家不是叛徒，你一公布，把人家的政治生命枪毙了，不管是什么观点，二七观点的也好，造总观点的也好，不同于御用工具，牛鬼蛇神，要负法律责任。另一个真正叛徒，你先告诉了他这一条，怎么对付，那一条怎么作，你先告诉了他。好人你们冤枉了，坏人把你们的秘密公布了，要好好分析一下，我找人和你们联系，先把那几条学一下。","index":189,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0817fd0bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（战斗师：革联、粮院联委、革委会东方红都与大叛徒有关系）","index":190,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"569dc3c95f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你说你不宣布，又宣布了，当面答应不印，回去为了派别的需要又印了，你连这个都不懂了，不要捕风追影，掉以轻心，信口开河。","index":191,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4548c2992","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：在这个问题上，有的造反派由于不了解情况，吸收了一个历史不清的人，作结合对象，这是常有的，你们河造总不至于没有吧？问题是，不能因一个人就说这个组织是叛徒组织，那些人，不能因为一个人牵连整个组织，革命小将不晓得么！我们反复讲，那是他的个人问题么！不是你们的责任，不要抓对立面的辫子。彭罗陆杨过去我们不是也不知道么，也还在中央工作过，我们的党内也有混入的叛徒，投机分子，特务。不然的话，你捉出一个来说你的组织如何如何，我捉出来一个说我的组织如何如何。揪出是好事，不要以此攻击，混入我党的也有薄一波、安子文、刘澜涛、杨献珍。革命组织中混入坏人也不要灰溜溜的，要挺起腰杆子，革命是革命的，反革命是反革命的。","index":192,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8beaa6b400","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：革委会我们有材料，你们再给我们一些材料，这个不要讲了，哪个组织也不敢保证（战斗师继续讲）。你讲了半天，前途还是没有讲么！（战斗师不听）你还是谈这，你不是讲前途吗？（战斗师提出要让纪登奎、文敏生站起来时），不要采取这个办法，不要采取斗的办法（生气地）你还是说过去的，我要中止你的发言了！不是要讲前途吗？你听我讲，你们闯了中南海的门，我们见了你们，搞了一天多，头一次嘛，进来还是守纪律的，坐在草地上学习毛主席语录，我让他们进到屋子里来，他们不进来，我看外面太冷了，给他们水喝，劝到小礼堂去的么！我是没有说的，后来传出去了，两方都知道了，他们就抓住这个小辫子，你们把这个问题看得过于严重了。主席批评了安徽问题，说冲了没有什么，中南海、国防部都冲了，不要看得太严重了，不要请罪了。要说不是错误也不行，不是错误，大家都去冲了。四月六日发了十条以后，冲的事情多了，第一要见要负责人，第二我们下了命令，卫戍司令部不得开枪，最近两个月冲得多了，不但是见负责人了，只是要见负责人，军队也不会打的，四川打架是不对的，青海是反革命政变了，内蒙犯了严重错误。前几天，江西冲军区夺枪了，我们劝他们，后来还了，是好的。中央通令是有时间性的。犯了错误，不要抓住不放，不应该冲的就不要冲，随便冲不对，路口也堵了，领导机关不要看得太严重了，群众也不要来找事，每一件事都要一分为二，河南乱出一个好的局面，只要大家努力军区已经认识了，调来了几个野战军的同志，都来了，都有认识了。你们把六条学习了，三方面达成一个协议，不要写得太长，一、不要示威游行，二、不要互打互冲，再加一点，不要停工停产。现在许多厂在停产。还有一条，不要阻拦铁路公路运输，不要扒车卧轨，你们达成协议的文字打电报回去（老保喊让我们撤除工事）","index":193,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ed4fd0b48","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：不要急，你怀疑我，我怀疑你，彼此不相信，就是撤除了，也是会筑起来的。因为农民进城带枪要打他们，他们不敢放下。","index":194,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"411ba74956","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：给军区下命令， 不准动员农民带武器进城，民兵的枪支弹药，统统都封存起来，要建立互相信任，不要压倒一方，你们那样要求多了，就写这三条，军区，军分区要象江西一样，下命令责成军区人武装部、县城下命令，不准动员农民进城，河南军区行吗？（何运洪：好）只要不武斗，那些东西都要撤除的。问题还不在这，仅仅在于凶手，这个东西都会打人的（手指着烟灰缸），石头砖块都会打人的。这个要达成协议的（问康老），是不是还开下去？（各方都要求发言，战斗师还要求发言）你们发言一个钟头了，各讲十分钟吧，从十分钟就可以看出各派的倾向性了，各派的水平了。","index":195,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1152c723f","type":"paragraph","text":"二七：（发言……）","index":196,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d2a33ec7e0","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：时间超过了一分钟，遵守总理的指示嘛，河造总也只能超过一分钟，（将二七发言稿要去）","index":197,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76af43d6fb","type":"paragraph","text":"（十大总部发言时）","index":198,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3df281dd3f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们共同达成协议，搞一个联合发言。战斗师你们回去想一想！","index":199,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"688a27ee13","type":"paragraph","text":"（十大总部互相争着发言）","index":200,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2aa08f44f","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：刚才你们有个条子，不能把八大总部看成一个总部，你们回去商量一下，今天时间到了，军区还要讲，省委干部还要讲，明天还要再搞一次，战斗师明天发言。","index":201,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c40928ea46","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我有两个比较紧的事，今天，有一部分冲开封市革命委员会筹备委员会对立起来了，我们希望八·二四打电话回去，八·二四说：电话不通），我们给你们叫。","index":202,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32744d1e2d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：一定要按照周总理指示去讲，不要添枝加叶的（对八·二四）。","index":203,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7841038aa","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：十大总部，实际是八大总部，听说军区支持二七公社，八大总部就冲军区了，他们的办法是轮换班搞。","index":204,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eac4852ff2","type":"paragraph","text":"（十大总部否认）","index":205,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4c6715128","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：不管那个总部都要退出来。","index":206,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce3a6ac234","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们不能主观，说没有冲，我还听说不光冲了，还将一个刘副司令员搞走了。","index":207,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a8bd4a1d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（老保不承认）（余嗣贵站起来说：有！一个是撤出来，第二要把刘副司令员放回来。（老保造谣说：二七公社抢赤卫队衣服）","index":208,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b4469394db","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天有一点外事，缅甸刺伤我们的人，还要去接，有些兄弟党明天下午还来，明天时间怎么分配，以后再通知你们。","index":209,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54b6b73d67","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：记者站，联络员回去把协议搞好，浙江的搞了一个很好嘛！拿给他们去看看。","index":210,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4b07c8bab1","type":"paragraph","text":"（老保攻击我们说：二七公社煽动农民不交公粮）","index":211,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e68ecf3000","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们刚才这个同志不是说公粮收的很好么？！","index":212,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"af8fa723ec","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}